# Wargio — Testing Standards

## Coverage Minimum

```
Backend total: ≥ 80% (API routes 100%, intent handlers 90%, MCP 80%)
Frontend total: ≥ 70% (Chat component 90%, API calls 85%)
```

## Struktur Test

```
tests/
├── unit/          — test per intent (min 5-10 cases each) + fuzzy_matching + schema
├── integration/   — mcp_connection, full_sale_flow, debt_lifecycle, agent_session
└── e2e/           — chat_api, production_url smoke tests
```

## Setiap Intent Wajib Punya

- Happy path test
- Min 2 edge case test
- Min 1 error case test

## Hari 6 Stress Test (Wajib Pass)

- Nama produk tidak lengkap → konfirmasi
- Capslock, fuzzy match, input kosong, multi-intent
- Qty 0/negatif → reject
- Stok 0 + penjualan → reject + suggest restock
- Customer nama mirip → disambiguasi
- MCP down → fallback message, tidak crash
- 2 sesi berbeda → tidak cross-contaminate
